Africa Sports d'Abidjan bụ klọb nwere ọtụtụ egwuregwu nke dị na obodo Abidjan, Ivory Coast
Sery Mogador malitere otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ahụ na aha 1947.
Ndị otu egwuregwu klọb ahụ na egwuregwu nke track and field, handball, basketball, na otu egwuregwu bọọlụ
N'ime ndị a, otu bọọlụ ha bụ nke a ma ama
Ha na-egwuri egwu na Stade Champroux
Klọb ahụ na-egwuri egwu ugbu a na Ligue 2.
Africa Sports bụ otu egwuregwu bọọlụ kachasị nwee ọganihu na Côte d'Ivoire, n'esonye ASEC Mimosas.
Na 6 Disemba 1992, ha ghọrọ otu egwuregwu nke mbụ na Ivory Coast nke meriri iko ndị mmeri nke ịkọ asọmpi nke Afrịka mgbe ha meriri Vital'O FC.
